\pard\f0\fs28   ({\b a}) Subsp. {\b ranunculoides}: Leaves all flat, the lower narrowly lanceolate or oblong-spathulate, distinctly petiolate, the upper ovate, acuminate. 2n = 42.{\i  Throughout the range of the species}.
